snippet.title: Houses of Barovia Chapter 12 - The Amber Temple
snippet.description:
"Greetings weary traveller. Come in, Come in, pull up a chair and warm yourself by the fire. Take a load off those feet! Err... claws…. hooves? It doesn’t matter!

From whatever realm you hail, here ALL are welcome

For you have stumbled into the Tavern of Tales, friend, our very own inter-dimensional watering hole. Either by fate, or by choice, you are in for a spectacular evening.

I’m sure you’ve heard of Baxter, the esteemed patron of this establishment. He’s a spell caster of some renown after all. Just don’t stare too long when you see him.

Tonight we have a very special treat for all those gathered here. A tale from a place spoken only in hushed tones. Barovia. Or is it?
 
For in the Barovia we’re going Strahd is not king and five powerful vampire houses preside over the land. This place removed from time can only be entered via death, as our heroes discovered first hand.

So sit back, and grab a drink as tonight we join friends old and new, as alliances shift and friendships form, and perhaps if we're lucky find those thought lost along the way.

The Tavern of Tales presents Houses of Barovia, with political intrigue, dangerous monsters, seductive vampires, and honestly some inane nonsense along the way.

I'll turn this one over to The Teller of Tales. Well met, friend. Enjoy." 

- Byrus, overworked barkeep of the Taven of Tales


Houses of Barovia is live streamed on Twitch Sundays at 4pm PST (7pm EST) on Twitch.tv/thetavernoftales 

All VODs will be uploaded following the stream. Initially they will be un-edited and then re-uploaded shortly after with portions edited.
